I've invited you to fill out a form:
Saarang 2017 Volunteers
<
_G4MUA3FBaN7CQ/viewform?cD0&wD1&uspDmail_form_link
Fill this form in to apply to be a volunteer for Saarang 2017. You may fill
the form in any number of times to apply to any number of departments.

The deadline for filling in the form is 4102016.
Volunteers will have the opportunity to work within the department for
which they are selected. As a volunteer it is still possible to take part
in the various events at Saarang and your work will be scheduled
accordingly.

For queries visit the contact us page at www.saarang.org

After filling in the form you will be contacted by the cores of the
departments to which you have applied after your end semester exams.


